Notebook de nettoyage des données OpenFoodFacts¶

Spécifier manuellement le type des colonnes en fonction de la documentation¶

# read first line to get column name
f = open("./data/en.openfoodfacts.org.products.csv", "r")
column_list = f.readline().split('\t')
f.close()
dtype_list = {}
for c in column_list:
    if c.endswith('_t'):
        dtype_list[c] = 'str'  # converted after
    elif c.endswith('_datetime'):
        dtype_list[c] = 'str'  # converted after
    elif c.endswith('_tags'):
        dtype_list[c] = 'str'
    elif c.endswith('_en') or c.endswith('_fr'):
        dtype_list[c] = 'str'
    elif c.endswith('_100g'):
        dtype_list[c] = 'float'
    elif c.endswith('_serving'):
        dtype_list[c] = 'float'
    elif c.endswith('_score'):
        dtype_list[c] = 'float'
    else:
        dtype_list[c] = 'str'

Normalisation des données textuelles¶

# Colonnes non null!
# remplir par 'unknown' (format tag) pour les valeurs null
colonnes_text = ['quantity', 'product_name', 'pnns_groups_1', 'pnns_groups_2']
for c in colonnes_text:
    final_df[c] = final_df[c].fillna('unknown').apply(lambda x : unidecode(str(x).lower()))

# Colonnes non null!
# remplir par 'unknown:unknown' (format tag) pour les valeurs null
colonnes_text = ['brands_tags', 'categories_tags', 'labels_tags', 'countries_tags', 'main_category']
for c in colonnes_text:
    final_df[c] = final_df[c].fillna('en:unknown').apply(lambda x : unidecode(str(x).lower()))

# remplir par une chaine vide pour les valeurs null
colonnes_text = ['ingredients_text', 'additives_tags']
for c in colonnes_text:
    final_df[c] = final_df[c].fillna('').apply(lambda x : unidecode(str(x).lower()))

msno.matrix(final_df)

_columns = ['fat_100g', 'saturated-fat_100g', 'carbohydrates_100g', 'sugars_100g', 'fiber_100g', 'proteins_100g', 'salt_100g', 'sodium_100g', 'fruits-vegetables-nuts-estimate-from-ingredients_100g']

# Reduire proportionnellement  graisse, gluscides, fibres, proteines et sel dont la somme est superieur √† 100g
_columns = ['fat_100g', 'carbohydrates_100g', 'fiber_100g', 'proteins_100g', 'salt_100g']
_sum = (final_df['fat_100g'] + final_df['carbohydrates_100g'] + final_df['fiber_100g'] + final_df['proteins_100g'] + final_df['salt_100g'])
_df = final_df.loc[_sum > 100, _columns]
_size = _sum[_sum > 100].shape[0]
print(f"Nombre de lignes dont la somme est >100 : {_size}")

if (_size):
    _df['sum'] = _sum
    _df['fat_100g'] = (_df['fat_100g'] / _df['sum'] * 100 * 100).astype(int)/100
    _df['carbohydrates_100g'] = (_df['carbohydrates_100g'] / _df['sum'] * 100 * 100).astype(int)/100
    _df['fiber_100g'] = (_df['fiber_100g'] / _df['sum'] * 100 * 100).astype(int)/100
    _df['proteins_100g'] = (_df['proteins_100g'] / _df['sum'] * 100 * 100).astype(int)/100
    _df['salt_100g'] = (_df['salt_100g'] / _df['sum'] * 100 * 100).astype(int)/100

    final_df.loc[_df.index, _columns] = _df[_columns]
    ((final_df['fat_100g'] + final_df['carbohydrates_100g'] + final_df['fiber_100g'] + final_df['proteins_100g'] + final_df['salt_100g']) > 100).value_counts()

print('    done')
